OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start, but cloudy skies
OL,6,Falready across the south of the region
OL,7,Fwill continue to spread north with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain reaching southern
OL,9,Fcounties during the evening. Becoming
OL,10,Frather breezy later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOften cloudy with further
OL,13,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,14,Frain and drizzle. Strengthening winds
OL,15,Fwill herald a band of heavy rain later
OL,16,Fin the night. Risk of coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
